    {
      "name": "09 \u2014 Cohort API (POST)",
      "description": "Cohort API cho chi ti\u1ebft h\u01a1n Master API cohort KPIs.\nPOST with JSON body. Auth via header.\n\n\u26a0\ufe0f Rate limit: 5 calls/min.\n\u26a0\ufe0f Ch\u1ec9 1 KPI per call (t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 functions tr\u1ea3 v\u1ec1).",
